            2000/-, Corporate Member: Rs. 5000/-<br />
            <span class="font-semibold">Foreigner</span>: Student Member: USD 50/-, Member USD
            100/-, Corporate Member: USD 200/-
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            <span class="font-semibold">Membership</span> fee may be paid for
            <span class="font-semibold">one</span>, <span class="font-semibold">two</span> or
